---
description: Always read agent rulebooks before edits
---

Before making **any code changes** in this repository:

1) Read **all** markdown files in `agent_rules/`:
- `agent_rules/AGENTS.md`
- `agent_rules/THEMING_RULEBOOK.md`
- `agent_rules/ARCHITECTURE.md`
- `agent_rules/API_DESIGN_RULES.md`
- `agent_rules/LOCALIZATION_RULES.md`
- `agent_rules/REPO_AUDIT_SUMMARY.md`

2) Follow those rules for:
- theming precedence and token usage (`theme.appThemeTokens`)
- design token consistency (`JDimens`, `JGaps`, `JInsets`)
- localization ownership and fallback order
- public API stability (exports from `lib/j_flutter_ui.dart`)

